{"tid":2513792,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–攻擊細菌的病毒","createTime":"2021-05-02T21:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T23:44:31.000Z","uid":38861,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1fe2cb753619d4509561064fde7a3fe5480d6b","tid":2513792,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T21:52:26.000Z","msg":"有能力消滅細菌的病毒，我們會稱之為Bacteriophage，又或者是Phage。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP1zKaFGGzgG53H624Nz8gE3vhwP6uGPCUEnXsJL9gFaL?filename=0P8xerR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0P8xerR.jpg&h=5fbee48d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2)DNA可以統稱由四個英文字母的不同組合而成，A、T、C、G。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbpnQUJMW5pkTsjWQtKg4rs8gFNPtdLme52eaWAtnjhCV?filename=mAYxerU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAYxerU.jpg&h=1fec096a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科學家發現，某特定品種Bacteriophage的DNA其英文字母的組合是由Z、T、C、G組成，常見的A被轉換成為Z。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)從圖中可見，Bacteriophage的ZT組合比AT組合多出一道Hydrogen Bond連繫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbaHwW2KycgEc5DEyjE1ETPnjkL1bzaKDRWXTXAsNvKQ5?filename=fHHxYTB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHHxYTB.png&h=c83b304f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細菌對抗外敵的其中一道手段就是切斷外來入侵者的DNA，而基於Bacteriophage擁有與別不同的DNA，細菌們辨認A的蛋白酶沒能夠辨認Bacteriophage的Z，因此亦少了一道手段對抗Bacteriophage的入侵。<br />\n<br />\n情形就像是男扮女裝的變態佬走進女廁一樣，透過改變自身的外貌來企圖掩菌耳目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=678415a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=238054da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-021-01157-x#ref-CR1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-021-01157-x%23ref-CR1&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=42db11d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-021-01157-x#ref-CR1</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/372/6541/512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F372%2F6541%2F512&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=fa94b0f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/372/6541/512</a>"},{"pid":"857260b789f1e0ad2e06726b0b3553905284746d","tid":2513792,"uid":191956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4350fd62c0a66759b5f991720c97e9875f185a6f","tid":2513792,"uid":247510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/by